=Episode 14=
(Look at Me!)

62
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,560
Xiao Rang.

63
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,360
Last night I saw you
staring at the book like this.

64
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,840
